line_1: Blest Jove! whose Pow'r must Nature's Laws enforce;
line_2: From whose Abyss, and rich unempty'd Source

line_1: What Crimes can I have wrought t'enforce
Not that I mean t' approve, or would inforce
Will need no stress of argument t' inforce
line_2: Th' expedience of a less advent'rous course.
